csw.services.location.commons

Class ClusterAwareSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.services.location.commons.ClusterAwareSettings

  • public class ClusterAwareSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    ClusterAwareSettings represents ClusterSettings with default values. Other helper methods from ClusterSettings can be used to add properties like port, seedNodes etc. ClusterAwareSettings is used internally in spawning many csw apps like csw-cluster-seed, csw-config-client-cli, csw-config-server, etc.
